Developer Terms of Use
des: Have you ever wondered where the cats go when the witches they loved and served are no more? Welcome to Crazy Cat Castle, where the souls of these furry familiars, are trapped, in limbo, forever seeking the Tiny Tuna of Teenytuck, the only power in the universe that can free them! Will you help them? If you dare! Note, this game is for mature audiences only!
